==English==

===Etymology===
From ''[[health]]'' + suffix ''[[-y]]''

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-healthy.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Adjective===
'''healthy'''

# enjoying health and vigor of body, mind, or spirit: [[well]]
#:''He was father to three '''healthy''' daughters.''
# conducive to [[health]]
#:A '''healthy''' diet and exercise can help to maintain proper weight.''
# evincing [[health]]
#:''She unwrapped the sandwich and took a '''healthy''' bite out of the middle.''

